Introduction: Dear participant, This survey aims to test how consumers use digital wallets and how comfortable they feel when using cryptocurrency.  The survey should take approximately 30 minutes to complete.  We will ask you to: 1. Watch a video and follow the instructions to install a cryptocurrency wallet browser extension and create a digital wallet. This wallet will used for testing only, no real money is involved. 2. Watch a video and follow the instructions to mine pseudo-cryptocurrency into your digital wallet. 3. Watch a video and follow the instructions for using the data qualtrics marketplace platform. 4. Create an online auction for your information.  Important: This survey is completely anonymous and will not record any of your personal information. In no way we will ask or receive access to your personal details or digital assets. You may choose to exit the experiment whenever you wish.
